-- Data types

int
varchar

Timestamp => TIMESTAMP default NOW() on UPDATE NOW()
=> while inserting gives current timestamp, and updates whenever the record is updated
=> NOW() can be replaced with CURRENT TIMESTAMP()


decimal(param1, param2) => param1: max total digits (before and after), param2: max digits after decimal 
eg: decimal(3,1) => 12.5, 22.3, 43.2, 1.2



